itution","kjv_def":"instrumentality","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"disposition(1x), ordinance(1x)"},"G1228":{"id":"G1228","lemma":"διάβολος","translit":"diábolos","derivation":"from G1225 (διαβάλλω);","strongs_def":"a traducer; specially, Satan (compare H07854)","kjv_def":"false accuser, devil, slanderer","pos":"adjective","usage":"devil(35x), slanderer(1x)"},"G1268":{"id":"G1268","lemma":"διανέμω","translit":"dianémō","derivation":"from G1223 (διά) and the base of G3551 (νόμος);","strongs_def":"to distribute, i.e. (of information) to disseminate","kjv_def":"spread","pos":"verb","usage":"spread(1x)"},"G1207":{"id":"G1207","lemma":"δευτερόπρωτος","translit":"deuteróprōtos","derivation":"from G1208 (δεύτερος) and G4413 (πρῶτος);","strongs_def":"second-first, i.e. (specially) a designation of the Sabbath immediately after the Paschal week (being the second after Passover day, and the first of the seven Sabbaths intervening before Pentecost)","kjv_def":"second … after the first","pos":"adjective"},"G1255":{"id":"G1255","lemma":"διαλαλέω","translit":"dialaléō","derivation":"from G1223 (διά) and G2980 (λαλέω);","strongs_def":"to talk throughout a company, i.e. converse or (genitive case) publish","kjv_def":"commune, noise abroad","pos":"verb","usage":"commune(1x)"},"G1231":{"id":"G1231","lemma":"διαγινώσκω","translit":"diaginṓskō","derivation":"from G1223 (διά) and G1097 (γινώσκω);","strongs_def":"to know thoroughly, i.e. ascertain exactly","kjv_def":"(would) enquire, know the uttermost","pos":"verb","usage":"enquire(1x)"},"G1289":{"id":"G1289","lemma":"διασπείρω","translit":"diaspeírō","derivation":"from G1223 (διά) and G4687 (σπείρω);","strongs_def":"to sow throughout, i.e. (figuratively) distribute in foreign lands","kjv_def":"scatter abroad","pos":"verb"},"G1261":{"id":"G1261","lemma":"διαλογισμός","translit":"dialogismós","derivation":"from G1260 (διαλογίζομαι);","strongs_def":"discussion, i.e. (internal) consideration (by implication, purpose), or (external) debate